1. *Teže* je raditi noću nego danju. (It is harder to work at night than during the day.)
2. Njegovi poslovi su mu *teži* od njenih. (His tasks are harder than hers.)
3. *Težilo* mu je da izađe iz kuće. (He struggled to leave the house.)
4. Oni se *teže* prilagođavaju promenama. (They adapt more slowly to changes.)
5. Ona je pokušala da podignu dizalicu, ali je bilo *teško*. (She tried to lift the lift, but it was difficult.)